Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.43,0:00:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.54,0:00:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.06,0:00:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是把真相告訴鳴人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事怎麼可能說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.47,0:00:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 你太小看鳴人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到佐助了 阿飛也在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位停一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 幹嗎停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.25,0:00:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊形已經確認過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙 把佐助的精確位置告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正北兩點鐘方向
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.02,0:00:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方一公里處 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.83,0:00:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉各位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:01:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是打算讓大家昏睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐井
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻似乎打算獨自去找佐助作個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.57,0:01:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要一個人去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.85,0:01:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我們不是約好大家一起的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.83,0:01:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來不允許任何人通過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.31,0:01:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.54,0:01:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就覺得這傢伙很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是佐助還是阿飛 僅靠我們都無法取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經跟卡卡西老師說好要阻止你們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.11,0:01:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.99,0:01:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐井 我只說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.87,0:01:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趕緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況有點不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不會讓你們去的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍法.超獸偽畫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想用蛇來綁住我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白卡卡西老師的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.23,0:02:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但怎能一直讓佐助肆意妄為呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.61,0:02:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要作個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.05,0:02:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 赤丸 別怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來還是狗更聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少它能明白我的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了 小李
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西就用通牙來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好地替我作了掩護啊 牙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.25,0:02:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:02:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連牙和小李都…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我中招了 請抓緊時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得不錯啊 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是什麼時候開始喜歡上佐助的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的我對超酷的佐助無比憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是覺得很帥而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位聽我說 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有喜歡的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜猜是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別告訴我是佐助哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 接下來是第七班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春野櫻 漩渦鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後還有宇智波佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著我和佐助成為了同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是春野櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:05:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說喜歡的東西 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不如說喜歡的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…將來的夢想也要說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為第七班…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有兩個鈴鐺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的課題就是在中午之前從我這奪走它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午之前沒能奪走鈴鐺的傢伙不給吃午飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 佐助 老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 現在察覺不到那傢伙的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午得三人一起搶鈴鐺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是拖後腿的話 我也會很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合格 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者應該領悟話中的玄機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在忍者世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不守規則的傢伙是個垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不珍惜同伴的傢伙則是垃圾中的垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使成為了同伴 我還是沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是單純喜歡帥氣的佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能看著他那帥氣的臉龐就滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.84,0:07:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那陰霾的表情之下隱藏了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從未考慮過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助一定會來找我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.74,0:08:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了尋求力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底對佐助做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是給了他離別的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.94,0:08:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 振作點 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總算明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是復仇者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.01,0:08:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是選擇將身體托付給惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一定要走向得到力量的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下你一個了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多陪我玩會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒印的事不准跟任何人提
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼如此逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不想再看見佐助如此痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.04,0:09:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你沒有關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籠罩著佐助的陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.66,0:10:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我察覺後為時已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻跟我交手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.98,0:10:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正想跟你較量一番呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:11:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是面對同村夥伴該使用的力度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算殺了鳴人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人察覺到了佐助內心的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.85,0:11:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 請不要礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺 鳴人成長了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經能直面佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被他們兩人拋在身後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 依舊沒能成長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你們不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一條道上的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.48,0:11:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常非常喜歡佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.25,0:11:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助如果能同我在一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會讓你後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都快快樂樂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對會讓你幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫你報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對會想盡一切辦法幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那還不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就帶上我一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然很煩人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助…請把佐助帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對會把佐助帶回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們一生的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不假思索便讓鳴人肩負重擔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:13:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一直在哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依賴著你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊隨著你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅靠自己什麼都…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等我一些時間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我也一起去…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了追上他們兩個 我也作出了努力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.49,0:13:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 佐助他…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踐踏了我們的信任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墮落到我們無法抵達的境地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便跟小櫻的約定取消也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己想救佐助 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了 我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.83,0:14:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會用這雙手將佐助…親自…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才真危險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了忍者世界 為了木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:15:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不能讓你們活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是裡四象封印術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 快遠離團藏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是把敵人吸進屍體裡一同封印的封印術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來他早就準備好這個能在自己死亡時發動的術式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來前往木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回收這傢伙的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 你也別太著急 先回根據地休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的瞳力使用過度了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去就沒法逞強了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻眼睛即將失去光明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只身前往又能如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要達成目的 忍耐也是必須的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 給你個忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要的話就乾脆點解決掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她知道我們太多事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.19,0:17:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然稱「我們」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼時候成你的同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.87,0:17:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 下次再會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人都在哪兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子連彈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我們一樣是地之書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼…眼鏡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想再見一次那時的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.02,0:19:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和過去完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真的是佐助嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你追來找我有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.06,0:19:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要跟佐助一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要脫離木葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了啊 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…我到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昏過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.21,0:21:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓大家操心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.82,0:21:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和隊長 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.97,0:21:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西老師和佐井已經出發了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.32,0:22:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我一起回村吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是卡卡西前輩的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷失的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.23,0:22:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻的事就交給前輩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.66,0:22:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠軍第一輪就出局了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.53,0:22:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 太不中用了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬥志精神不足啊 鬥魂在哪兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.10,0:22:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在對方的耳邊 輕聲細語
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.73,0:22:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳擊應當這樣 攻擊腰部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起 佐井 還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.47,0:22:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.53,0:22:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.86,0:22:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶貴的寫真袋被裝訂住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.21,0:22:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級想看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.22,0:22:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 無論怎樣都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.11,0:22:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.57,0:23:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.30,0:23:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒轍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐井給我起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣怎樣 扣人心弦的真相是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.95,0:23:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼狗屁寶物…還我錢來
